@import std://make.convo

> target
in: 'src/pg-schema-gen.js'
out: 'args.md'
model: 'gpt-5'
===
Convert the `Args` typedef to a markdown table used to document CLI arguments

Table columns: name, value, multi, description.

The multi column should be empty or have a "Y" character if the prop is an array type.

The value column should describe the logical value of the prop. For example an array of paths should have a value of "path".

Update the descriptions to be singular.

Remove `Ary` from the names of the props.

Convert the prop names to kebab-case with all lower cases and start the names with '--'.

Do not include undefined as part of the props type.

===